  "text": "[World Weather](https://world-weather.info)\nAdd the current city\nSearch\n  * Weather\n  * [Archive](https://world-weather.info/archive/)\n  * [Widget](https://world-weather.info/widget/)\n  * [METAR](https://world-weather.info/metar/)\n\n\n°F\n  * [World](https://world-weather.info/forecast/)\n  * [Japan](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/)\n  * [Tōkyō-to](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo_to/)\n  * [Weather in Tokyo](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/)\n\n\n# Weather in Tokyo, May 23\nWeather Forecast for May 23 in Tokyo, Tōkyō-to - temperature, wind, atmospheric pressure, humidity and precipitations. Detailed hourly weather chart.\n[ May 21 ](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/21-may/)[May 22](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/22-may/) Select date: ![Select a date](https://world-weather.info/images/menu-calend-op.png) [May 24](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/24-may/)[May 25](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/25-may/)\n## May 23, 2026   \n|   | Atmospheric conditions  \nand temperature °F  | Feels Like °F  | Atmospheric  \npressure inHg  | Wind speed  \nmph  | Humidity  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n| Night  | +57°  |  +57°  | 30  | 15.7  | 73%  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n| Morning  | +63°  |  +63°  | 30  | 15  | 65%  |  \n| Day  | +70°  |  +70°  | 30  | 11.4  | 55%  |  \n| Evening  | +63°  |  +63°  | 30  | 11.6  | 71%  |  \n  \n\n## May 23, 2025   \n|   | Atmospheric conditions  \nand temperature °F  | Feels Like °F  | Atmospheric  \npressure inHg  | Wind speed  \nmph  | Humidity  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n| Night  | +63°  |  +63°  | 29.6  | 15  | 79%  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n| Morning  | +63°  |  +63°  | 29.7  | 13.6  | 78%  |  \n| Day  | +73°  |  +73°  | 29.8  | 16.3  | 57%  |  \n| Evening  | +66°  |  +66°  | 29.8  | 14.8  | 63%  |  \n  \n\n### Bio-meteorological forecast\n  * Meteorological sensitivity index\n  * 3 \n  * Meteosensitive people are likely to experience weather-related symptoms.\n\n\n  * Geomagnetic conditions\n  * 2 \n  * Solar activity may affect some sensitive people.\n\n\n  * Influence of solar activity\n  * 3 \n  * High risk of harm from unprotected sun exposure due to UV radiation.\n\n\n  \n\n## Hourly forecast for May 23, 2025\nCreated with Highcharts 9.1.0TemperatureChart context menut Actualt RealFeelHumidity (%)Pressure00010203040506070809101112131415161718192021222356°64°72°80°05010015028293031Highcharts.com\n  \n\n## May 23, 2024   \n|   | Atmospheric conditions  \nand temperature °F  | Feels Like °F  | Atmospheric  \npressure inHg  | Wind speed  \nmph  | Humidity  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n| Night  | +64°  |  +64°  | 29.9  | 8.9  | 92%  |  \n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |  \n| Morning  | +68°  |  +68°  | 29.8  | 7.6  | 80%  |  \n| Day  | +75°  |  +75°  | 29.8  | 13.9  | 67%  |  \n| Evening  | +72°  |  +73°  | 29.7  | 17.2  | 90%  |  \n  \n\n### Bio-meteorological forecast\n  * Meteorological sensitivity index\n  * 3 \n  * Meteosensitive people are likely to experience weather-related symptoms.\n\n\n  * Geomagnetic conditions\n  * 2 \n  * Solar activity may affect some sensitive people.\n\n\n  * Influence of solar activity\n  * 3 \n  * High risk of harm from unprotected sun exposure due to UV radiation.\n\n\n  * Influence of the phases of the moon\n  * 1 \n  * Insomniacs may be affected by the full moon, resulting in tiredness during the day.\n\n\n  \n\n## Hourly forecast for May 23, 2024\nCreated with Highcharts 9.1.0TemperatureChart context menut Actualt RealFeelHumidity (%)Pressure00010203040506070809101112131415161718192021222348°64°80°96°05010015028293031Highcharts.com\n  \n\n## Tokyo Weather Calendar for May\nSelect a date in Weather Calendar to find weather data for a specific day.\nSun\nMon\nTue\nWed\nThu\nFri\nSat\n[1](https://world-weather.info/forecast/japan/tokyo/01-may/)\n[2](h